Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The furthest space city from Earth,\Nknown as Side 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...proclaimed itself the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In roughly one month of fighting,\Nthe Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Federation Forces caused\Nthe deaths of half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if they're civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get me some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my Yuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get on board the White Base!\N- Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fraw Bow! Get to the White Base! Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro? Are you in that mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go! Soon, there'll be no air left here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! I'll take over!\NPlease return to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only a pilot cadet.\NCan you fire this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can certainly try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed my orders, as well as Denim's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about, Slender.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Federation mobile suit has\Nthe kind of performance you describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand, sir. But I saw it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Open a laser communication channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Contact Vice Admiral Dozle.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- You'll be safe here on the ship. Just sit still.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You, down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tie bandages, right?\NCould you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to go look for\Nyour mothers later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Over there.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. We need your help over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please clean that wound and\Nget some suture tape on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure the Zeon ship has ceased fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You have my permission to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeon attack has wiped out\Nvirtually all defense personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Every soldier and engineer at\NSide 7 has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of just two Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the injured soldiers,\Nless than 10 are combat-ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all the Gundam components\Non board at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, we have one man\Npiloting a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He is transferring a Guncannon\Nand Guntank on board now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't confirmed his identity yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's finished, get the White Base\Naway from Side 7 at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. But the pilot of the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer can take us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- But sir...\N- Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm licensed to operate cruiser-class\Nspace gliders, if that helps any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai Yashima, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Of the famous Yashima family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were all set to celebrate the successful{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But since you dawdled and didn't show up,ing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've discovered the Federation's\NOperation V, Admiral Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Operation V?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. They've developed mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also identified a brand-new\NFederation battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char, the Red Comet, strikes again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We were on our way back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...so we've used up all our\Nmissiles and ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You need supplies, huh? You'll have them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.\NWe also need three more Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You lost three Zaku mobile suits?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Vice Admiral. Two were lost to\Na single Federation mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. You'll get your Zakus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want all the data you can get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And capture that mobile suit If possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I will try, sir.\N- Good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign! Get me three commandos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, aren't we going to wait\Nfor the supply ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In war, you must think two or three moves\Nahead of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Slender escaped from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Logically, we can do just the opposite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who's piloting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody called Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he was one of the pilots\Ntesting it at Side 7, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can contact the Gundam\Nusing the panel on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the Gundam cover the White Base\Nwhen it leaves port.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the channel control?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be there, on the right console.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai, how goes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the basic operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the engine control...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu can search for trained personnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...if anyone comes back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really the Gundam's cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child!\NSome kid is piloting the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- That's Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look for yourself.\NThis boy is in the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's no pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?\NHow can a child pilot the Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- That boy...!\N- You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him well, but at Side 7\Nhe's well-known for his love of machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that boy the one who\Ntook down Zeon's Zakus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only able to beat them\Nthanks to the Gundam's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- What are you doing there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the person who ordered\Nme to load the Gundam components.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll remove him, Captain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only If we have any surviving pilots...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- You take the residential block.\N- Right. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chief. You can make it.\NHey, what are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain's ordered us to\Nlook for anyone left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!\NAre there any other people left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me. I was busy avoiding blasts\Nand barely made it here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself a man? Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A coward like you ought to be\Nleft here at Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at you on your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you. You're Say... Sayla, right?\NSomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking to me\Nlike some kind of street punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw Bow!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey you! Give us a hand.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate engines, 3 percent thrust.\NMega particle cannons, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Target Side 7's space gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But avoid direct hits to the docking bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Slender.\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- We can enter via this maintenance airlock.\N- All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do about Amuro, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's attacking us?\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The same Musai-class warship approaching\N40 degrees port-stern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy any of the Gundam\Ncomponents that we can't use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Issue a beam rifle to the Gundam.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit young to go into battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But historically, there have been\N15-year-old soldiers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the Gundam components\Nleft at Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? There're enough parts for three more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let the Zeons find out our secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's odd...\NThe Musai's falling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling back?\NAmuro, do you know what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could use that "super napalm" thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's judgment is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship will launch soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone left here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I'm going to Amuro's!nner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone left, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any survivors here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Any survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No survivors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like a soldier or a guerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take off the helmet!\NAnd face the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But... she's too strong...\N...to be Artesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a Zeon soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...My brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to use the super napalm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please climb onto my hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're destroying all of the\Nmobile suit parts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro. You're sure It was a Zeon soldier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lie down in the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Are you all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! A Zeon soldier\Njust entered the space port!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Close all hatches on the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those who can hold a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands! Fire on the Zeon soldier\Napproaching the bow! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All members of scouting party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please launch immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lt. Commander!\N- They're right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fire. I'm going to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lt. Commander!\N- Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move, you're more likely to be hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Small targets like humans\Naren't so easy to hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Musai! Do you read? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Is the Musai. We have identified you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's moving out.\NUse the laser line...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and launch my Zaku and Slender's\Nwith type 1 equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Roger.\N- Prepare to launch Zakus! Heading RD23.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gate sensor, 360 degrees,\Nall roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The computer'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hailing Amuro, in the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too far from the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay within 10 km to starboard of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Check that each block is airtight.\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Operators.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our helmsman is a rookie.\NGive her time to respond to directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine output gage is to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Keep it out of the red zone.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Missile stores are shown on the indicator...\N- I know. This one here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You catch on quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All blocks! Prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving the docking bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase main engine power!\NHard to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright!hter okay to launch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, are you sure you can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course. I'm a pilot cadet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's better than a complete\Nnovice. Any flight experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two simulations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's basically the same as Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,High-intensity heat sources approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Missiles?\N- Large missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Evasive maneuvers!\N12 degrees to port, 8 degrees down!\N- Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Y-Yes, sir!\N- Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got them! Let me shoot them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Go to it!\N- I'm launching now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These, I can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two more objects approaching the ship!\N- What are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Looks like mobile suits, sir.\N- Zakus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Mr. Bright, no Zaku\Nis capable of that speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One Zaku is approaching\Nat three times the normal speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Comet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Char, the Red Comet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Battle of Loum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...Char single-handedly\Ndestroyed five of our battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Let's test the performance\Nof the Federation's mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him!\NA Zaku is not a human! Even I can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Amuro! You're not ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! That was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So this is battle...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast! What maneuverability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Slender? Get behind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander! What is that?!\NHe has a new weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares, as long as it doesn't hit us!\NCover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Core Fighter will cover you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't deplete the beam rifle's energy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to be told that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behind you! Ascend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Slender!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One shot... Destroyed in one shot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that mobile suit equipped with\Na battleship-class beam cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A Zaku... w-with one shot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a new type of fighter. Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The beam rifle's energy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I used it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't match that firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam has returned to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the loading is finished,\Nhave Ryu and Amuro report to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the White Base on course for Luna II.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel must remain at their stations\Nand alternate rest shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright, status on the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't moved. But, knowing Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...they will come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You rely too much on\Nthe Gundam's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be more efficient in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you were assigned to the Gundam,\Nyou became a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty is to protect the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it,\Nbut that's the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't handle it,\Nthen go back to Side 7 now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't promise that I'm up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go deal with the Gundam's maintenance!\NUse whomever you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you're responsible for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna II...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An asteroid placed in\Nthe moon's orbital path...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...to provide construction\Nmaterials for the space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is now the location...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Federation's front-line base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As Char's Musai takes on supplies...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam and the Core Fighter take\Nthis opportunity to launch an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Zeon has soldiers\Naside from Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The thunderous roar of the battle rages.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode... Vote to Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vote to Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:54.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:59.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:09.63,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:14.55,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:19.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:24.56,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:29.15,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:39.45,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:54.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:59.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:09.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:14.55,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:19.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:24.56,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:29.15,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:39.45,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
